content:
For real, get over to monitoring. Once you have better monitoring so many things fall into place. You can work for 12 hours easy. No breaks no problem. And you won’t lose the plot of how things should sound. You’ll be unleashed.

@Nomograph Mastering is a sage at this, listen to him. His knowledge is hard won, don’t get in your own way and convince yourself it’s a breaks thing.

Like Ruairi says you can do a lot with a little heart and energy even if you don’t have the cash yet
